Title: An Act Changing the Name of Talogtog Elementary School in Barangay Kimmalaba Municipality of Dolores Province of Abra, to Kimmalaba Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 210
An Act Changing the Name of Talogtog Elementary School in Barangay Kimmalaba Municipality of Dolores Province of Abra, to Kimmalaba Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Talogtog Elementary School in Barangay Kimmalaba, Municipality of Dolores, Province of Abra, is hereby changed to Kimmalaba Elementary School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 25, 1982
